@startuml
title LowCortisol WebApp - Notification Frontend Bounded Context Layers
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

package "Notification Frontend Bounded Context" {
  class "Domain" as Frontend_notification_Domain <<layer>>
  class "Application" as Frontend_notification_Application <<layer>>
  class "Infrastructure" as Frontend_notification_Infrastructure <<layer>>
  class "Presentation" as Frontend_notification_Presentation <<layer>>
}

Frontend_notification_Presentation ..> Frontend_notification_Application : user actions / state
Frontend_notification_Application ..> Frontend_notification_Domain : models and rules
Frontend_notification_Application ..> Frontend_notification_Infrastructure : API services / adapters
Frontend_notification_Infrastructure ..> Frontend_notification_Domain : resources and mappers
Frontend_notification_Presentation ..> Frontend_notification_Domain : view models

note bottom of Frontend_notification_Application
Detailed class diagrams for each layer are available in docs/diagrams/class/frontend/layers/notification.
end note

@enduml
